                          config.sys example himem dos high umb files buffers safe config sys baseline                                                                                    CONFIG.SYS example                                              Use HIMEM, DOS HIGH UMB, FILES 30, and BUFFERS 20 as the safe CONFIG SYS baseline.                                                                                                              batch file help exist checks clear status messages 8.3 dos-compatible names model files                                                                         Batch file help                                                 In a batch file, use IF EXIST checks, clear status messages, and 8.3 DOS-compatible names for model files.                                                                                      batch safety check exist before running large files print clear status lines step                                                                               Batch safety                                                    Check IF EXIST before running large files and print clear status lines for each step.                                                                                                           memory error dos free conventional unloading tsrs loading drivers high using smaller profile                                                                    DOS memory error                                                Free conventional memory by unloading TSRs, loading drivers high, or using a smaller profile.                                                                                                   